 之後番市區買手信， 住手信街附近民宿， 兩人一間房2xx蚊一晚包早餐共用廁所連洗衣機乾衣機。 第六日一早出機場番香港"},{"pid":"b8e0f35969afab9cc8a5e43cebdf3c26a95a75a8","tid":295754,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔渣車唔潛水 只係當去睇風景/景點可唔可行?</blockquote><br />\n可以， 當去澳門"},{"pid":"ef716724810138ea6e4f1689245dc6568e8b6662","tid":295754,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分享一下你既行程？<br />\n邊日渣車？<br />\n去左兩次沖繩都撞正打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都驚， 所以臨出發前幾日check哂無風無點落雨先租車訂房"},{"pid":"93756a6e38afa7390304790dd28c1093d3b1d9e3","tid":295754,"uid":112855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"我個陣同巴打個行程差唔多 但唔識揸車只好等巴士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e108cab58fcd7bba8da6a949f2b09c5326f901ec","tid":295754,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個陣同巴打個行程差唔多 但唔識揸車只好等巴士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nso sad,  等車好熱， 巴士冷氣又好弱。<br />\n揸車方便舒服慳時間好多<br />\n<br />\n學揸車啦， 學完再去"},{"pid":"361490d1fc917f4644798fafeb4da62d1a283f3d","tid":295754,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗渣車？</blockquote><br />\n睇日子人數時間，<br />\n就算要揸車既話， 一日都可以去齊所有景點。<br />\n時間多可以分幾日搭巴士去哂所有景點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多人/時間唔多， 租一日車<br />\n少人/時間多， 全程巴士<br />\n<br />\n租車同巴士5天券計落差唔多</blockquote><br />\n何謂時間多? <br />\n五日夠唔夠全用巴士玩?</blockquote><br />\n夠， 搭巴士兩日可以去哂所有景點， 其餘時間去其他島玩</blockquote><br />\n其他島行路就OK? <br />\n<br />\n咁係四晚都住哂係石垣?</blockquote><br />\n你budget幾多</blockquote><br />\n2000 兩人"},{"pi